<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><hymn_number>1154</hymn_number>
<author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
<title>yé sū shì nǐ 迦南1154</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 shì nǐ huà jiě le wǒ shēng mìng zhōng de xǔ duō yí hàn.
 shì nǐ fǔ píng suì yuè gěi wǒ liú xià de zhé zhòu shāng bān.
 shì nǐ qīn zì zǒu dào wǒ shēng mìng de zuì biān yuán.
 shì nǐ zài wǒ zuì gū dān de shí hòu qiāo qiāo yǔ wǒ wèi bàn.
 yé sū chú nǐ yǐ wài zài tiān shàng wǒ hái yǒu shéi,
 yé sū chú nǐ yǐ wài zài de shàng wǒ gèng wú ài liàn.
 suī rán wǒ de ròu tǐ hé xīn cháng shuāi cán,
 dàn nǐ què shì wǒ xīn lǐ de lì liàng, xiāng bàn zài měi yī tiān.</lyrics>
</song>